{"tid":2345924,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"DC決心挑戰Marvel 將推出6套英雄片","createTime":"2020-12-30T02:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T11:40:13.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc8bd95f5f04fd65db2e40979f77e7e993f639f","tid":2345924,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T02:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2Wg1Hzx8MjDjTiMO5Ib0MKdKDbg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P2KDVXVT2BCSPJ6VNEPBS7NAKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2Wg1Hzx8MjDjTiMO5Ib0MKdKDbg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP2KDVXVT2BCSPJ6VNEPBS7NAKY.jpg&h=709127ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華納兄弟近來有非常多舉動，最近旗下的DC就宣佈一連串新計劃，包括推出6套超級英雄片，並分別於戲院及HBO Max都會有新作，擺明挑戰Marvel與Disney+。<br />\n<br />\n近日DC電影公司主席Walter Hamada就宣佈重大計劃，表示4部大作將會於陸續於戲院上映，包括《神奇女俠3》（Wonder Woman）、《水行俠2》（Aquaman）、由「The Rock」狄維莊遜（Dwayne Johnson）主演的《Black Adam》與現正拍攝的《閃電俠》（The Flash），目標是自2022年，每年都推出新作。另外，其他DC角色作品就會於HBO Max推出，包括《Batgirl》與《Static Shock》等，目標是於HBO Max一年推出兩部DC電影。另外，DC亦會玩平行時空，例如羅拔柏迪臣（Robert Pattinson）是新蝙蝠俠，但同時在另一個平行時空的《閃電俠》中，米高基頓（Michael Keaton）及班亞弗力（Ben Affleck）才是蝙蝠俠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/V5NmH3wR8y7fWJoLgRan1UrCtyg=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QUHLQ2LSW5C5LLRGKHWHCPTPE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FV5NmH3wR8y7fWJoLgRan1UrCtyg%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQUHLQ2LSW5C5LLRGKHWHCPTPE4.jpg&h=8b685bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cZxIxgPb6cXYPAzb91KYYUm0ZbM=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GLY7CDTEBJGQDJ2G5WWXIICX4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcZxIxgPb6cXYPAzb91KYYUm0ZbM%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGLY7CDTEBJGQDJ2G5WWXIICX4Q.jpg&h=bf4b3494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/K1z-6ixQknejWC90Y3df-1ANorE=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N3UHLB33BVF6DI7IF3GVTNUFSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FK1z-6ixQknejWC90Y3df-1ANorE%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN3UHLB33BVF6DI7IF3GVTNUFSE.jpg&h=3f72be26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ja4ZkEQrIQDEU777jr3PHZdStUo=/802x501/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7ZNRMWNMLREBXDB7Y2Z7OVGARY.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fja4ZkEQrIQDEU777jr3PHZdStUo%3D%2F802x501%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7ZNRMWNMLREBXDB7Y2Z7OVGARY.jpeg&h=cd594846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Inr-52b7J2ALdJ8NDHY-nSCMoKg=/802x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/54Z7SFF4TVDA5NH2RSMTAMCXUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FInr-52b7J2ALdJ8NDHY-nSCMoKg%3D%2F802x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F54Z7SFF4TVDA5NH2RSMTAMCXUE.jpg&h=89c4e0cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1393370264c3b94bb620344baff54dad9ec4171c","tid":2345924,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T02:18:14.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" 